OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMostly cloudy throughout the
OL,6,Fday with the chance of a few light
OL,7,Fshowers. Rain will spread eastwards
OL,8,Fduring the evening. Fresh west to
OL,9,Fsouthwesterly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA cloudy evening with light
OL,12,Fand patchy rain. The rest of the night
OL,13,Fwill remain cloudy with rain turning
OL,14,Fshowery and occasionally heavy.
OL,15,FSouthwesterly winds becoming strong to
OL,16,Fgale force.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
