OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FCloudy at first with
OL,6,Foccasionally heavy rain clearing east.
OL,7,FThen turning brighter with a few
OL,8,Fscattered showers. Strong to near gale
OL,9,Fforce winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FBright
OL,12,For sunny spells on Sunday with a few
OL,13,Fscattered showers. Fairly unsettled
OL,14,Fand changeable later Monday into
OL,15,FTuesday with the risk of rain or
OL,16,Fshowers.
